comment: Bayless (MIL) and Monroe (MIL) maintain legal guarding position as they trap Lopez (BKN).
Middleton (MIL) changes his pivot foot prior to releasing his dribble.
Sloan (BKN) makes incidental contact with Middleton (MIL) that does not affect his RSBQ.
Milwaukee purposely makes contact with the ball after the made basket, which prevents the opposing team from quickly inbounding the ball.
Middleton (MIL) sets the screen on Lopez (BKN) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Kilpatrick (BKN) makes contact with Middleton (MIL) that affects his RSBQ.
McCullough (BKN) sets the screen on Inglis (MIL) without giving him room to avoid the contact.
